law.history: Repealed 2014 Ky. Acts ch. 92, sec. 314, effective January 1, 2015. -- Amended 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 255, sec. 31, effective July 15, 1998. -- Amended 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 164, sec. 52, effective June 17, 1978. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 2872b-4, 2896b-14, 3142b-18, 3351a-18.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Police and firefighters' pension fund in cities of the first, second, and third classes -- Exempt from process in some cases.
